        <p>Little Cranberry Island may be only 1 mile wide by 1.5 miles long, but that won't stop us creating a 26.2 and 13.1 mile course for the 2nd Annual Islesford Half Marathon. </p>
            <p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, August 4th @ 9 am (7:30 boat from NE Harbor)<br>
            <strong>Where:</strong>  Start at the end at the town field </p>
            <p>
Meet at Islesford Boatworks before the race to receive a number.</p>
            <p> We'd like to give a huge Boatworks thanks to Marilyn and the rest of Caroll family for organizing this event!</p>
